                                                        Saudi Basic Industries Corp(Sabic)                        

                            A slight quarter stumble
                        

                                                                                    SABIC reported a 25% decline in Q2 2017 net profit to SAR3.71bn from a revised SAR4.96bn a year earlier. H1 2017 Net profit amounted to SAR 8.9bn, a 13.6% YoY rise. H1 2017 revenue increased by 3.3% to SAR72bn compared to SAR69.73bn a year earlier.
                                                                        











