                                                Ste Euro Cycles SA
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            



Euro-Cycles is a Tunisia-based company specializing in the manufacture of bicycles and cycles exclusively for export. Euro Cycles manufactures beginners bikes and midrange in compliance with the specifications required by our customers bikes. Models manufactured cover a wide range of children's bikes (16 from 5 years) to adult bikes. The range includes several categories ranging from classic city bikes through the mountain bikes (MTB, BMX, among others).
	Sales Analysis. 
	Ste Euro Cycles SA reported sales of 80.31 million Dinar (US$33.86 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				an
			
			increase of 7.3%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 74.83 million Dinar.
	
			Sales at Ste Euro Cycles SA have increased during each of the previous five years
		
		(and since 2011, sales have increased a total of 66%).
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










